{"tid":1670114,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(自問月入50K 就入一入尼睇睇)【本土X國際戰線】鍾庭耀發起全港大型民調及公投(3)","createTime":"2019-10-23T01:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T00:52:55.000Z","uid":156096,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"18292f3cfcb1c1eb95bd57aa3cc99a90699a2251","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"Post(1)：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1659927/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1659927/page/1</a><br />\nPost(2)：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1669089/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1669089/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我地係一群熱愛香港的小市民<br />\n<br />\n首先，我地<strong><ins><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一個民調報告出左</span></span></ins></strong>，多謝大家支持﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191022/60182422\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F60182422&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=33602f91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F60182422&h=e9b6c098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191022/60182422</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DfGRVZa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDfGRVZa.jpg&h=88a36ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><em><strong>廢話唔多講</strong></em></span></ins>，我地做民調目的是要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">持續追蹤一些大核彈的民意</span></strong></span>，同時會按民意不斷換入新核彈<br />\n最後，鍾教授就會極合成一份完整的報告，在國際社會發報，向港共施壓，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">迫佢跪低同香港人瀨西及交出真相</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但，屌你老母</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你班連登仔知唔知我地仲未籌夠錢???</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無錢點做REPORT ??</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登仔又話個個一畢業50K ?? </span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地去撚晒邊??</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非撚同我即刻做齊下面三寶﹕</span></span></strong><br />\n1)在香港民意研究計劃網頁上<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">定期提交香港人想調查的核彈的民情 (我們會按不同時機不斷追蹤最強核彈和換入新核彈)</span></span></strong><br />\n2)幫手眾籌 (從10月17日起計至2019年12月底，所需要的費用大約為港幣<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>80萬元</strong></span></span></ins>，超額的話會用作2020年【我們香港人】的延續經費)<br />\n3) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Subscribe 香港民意研究所 Facebook 和 Youtube</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nLINK﹕<br />\n香港民意研究所 Facebook﹕​​​​​​​<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKPublicOpinionProgram/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKPublicOpinionProgram%2F&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=2631a2bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKPublicOpinionProgram/</a><br />\n香港民意研究所 Youtube﹕ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=0b1f3f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxNv1rm97xhk-3zN9kvAOKw</a><br />\n香港民意研究計劃 (香港民研) 網頁﹕<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/wehkers-index\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fwehkers-index&d=6Qw6l1jLXmk45E1e9I%2Bltltf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=d81a4de3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/wehkers-index</a> (<strong>有是次調查的簡介/報告﹑提交問題方法﹑眾籌LIN</strong>K)<br />\n<br />\n最後，補多句╴現在放棄的話 比賽就結束了!!!<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evFjkxd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevFjkxd.jpg&h=1c291a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8452477a91d754fcfea976c48ba1feac06bef091","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:37:24.000Z","msg":"快d入尼推post"},{"pid":"cb8d8cf97a43bcfc2a1df3e5cc10781ab62d1531","tid":1670114,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:37:43.000Z","msg":"冇50k 唔小心入左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7197bd911c482e55ca279cf1d423e1253984c470","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"吊你 100 幾10 都hi"},{"pid":"b01202a79cf1a41264b6de7495379158fa869237","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:39:11.000Z","msg":"吊你。。一百幾十都得架<br />\n人地幫你做國際文宣，連登仔只要比少少錢就得"},{"pid":"5224a1a5607f667c98c94a8a767e9fd6d40d3806","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a918ed0ff8f413f4acafd3a709e6bbd05cc57adb","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:42:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94f22cb90475274c952be598dec4bb546c4605f4","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9eb9db0da76fc6901a2af2d8ddaaa05146700a","tid":1670114,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:45:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9b7bd2790b944edc43d852a64fae71b9aaf9b62","tid":1670114,"uid":1